{"author":"Joe Oakhart","data":{"alias":"main-name-crowd","description":"# Pre-release codebase-health remediations (2026-07-02 joe-janitor audit)\n\n## Context\n\nA verified codebase-health audit (joe-janitor, 2026-07-02: 8 concern agents + temporal\npass, then 4 adversarial verification agents; 0 findings refuted) ran ahead of next week's\nwider release. Full report at `.joe-janitor/report-2026-07-02.md`. Overall health is good and\nimproved since the 2026-06-24 audit, but a Critical gate-bypass, several High structural/governance\nitems, and a set of Mediums warrant remediation before increased external scrutiny.\n\nThis epic is the umbrella for the remediation work. Children are created per finding as they are\napproved; the Critical (risk 1) and the completion-gate doc drift (risk 2) are remediated first.\n\n## Success Criteria\n\n- The Critical `ALLOW_LLM` gate bypass is fixed with a regression test; both shipped gate\n  workflows are detected by `has_llm_steps`.\n- Completion-gate docs match the post-`30c2ef3ad` child-closure semantics (blocking vs\n  certification-withholding); the \"unsigned close ⇒ validation failed\" biconditional is corrected.\n- Each approved remediation lands as its own child through Gerrit (LLM-Review + Verified),\n  with a `rebar-ticket:` trailer, plan-review at claim, and a signed completion verdict at close.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] Risk 1 (has_llm_steps ALLOW_LLM bypass) remediated + regression test; child closed.\n- [ ] Risk 2 (completion-gate child-closure doc drift) remediated; child closed.\n- [ ] Stale-reference doc/comment fixes (already landed) tracked under a child.\n- [ ] The remaining approved remediations are decomposed into children, each with AC + file-impact.\n- [ ] All children closed with signed completion verdicts; report's Critical/High set addressed.","id":"9322-f84a-e047-4471","parent_id":"","priority":1,"tags":[],"ticket_type":"epic","title":"Pre-release codebase-health remediations (2026-07-02 audit)"},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"CREATE","timestamp":1783053634713102001,"uuid":"118a728a-aeaa-4901-a3c5-b5484dc65542"}